      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable Lock limited-slip differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the structural and mechanical longevity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded poly-bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain performance is sharp, maintaining the linear power delivery and 8,000 RPM redline that define this analog driving icon.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and premium comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with leather seating that remains supple and free of rips or heavy bolster wear. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive touchscreen infotainment system, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is solid; it has a complete service history, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a brake pad replacement just 3,000 miles ago. The tires offer plenty of life for the seasons ahead. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This unit has been meticulously maintained, ensuring a driving experience that remains both smooth and responsive. With its refined interior and a clean, commanding exterior presence, this automobile offers exceptional value for those seeking a reliable yet distinguished daily driver. We invite you to experience the caliber of this well-preserved specimen firsthand.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really wonderful shape. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and has plenty of life left for its next owner. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that looks great on the road, this is definitely the one for you! I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true with recent control arm and bushing replacements. While the finish displays minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust, benefiting from consistent valve clearance adjustments and a strictly followed rod bearing service interval. Equipped with a limited-slip differential and M-tuned chassis, this vehicle offers the raw, analog feedback sought by purists.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
